              { day: "Day 2: Historic Churches of Old Goa & Spice Plantation", desc: "Visit the UNESCO World Heritage Basilica of Bom Jesus (housing the remains of St. Francis Xavier) and Se Cathedral. Enjoy a guided tour of a lush spice plantation in Ponda, including a traditional buffet lunch." },
