              { day: "Day 2: Solang Valley Adventure Sports & Rohtang Pass", desc: "Drive to Solang Valley for paragliding, zorbing, and quad-biking. If permits are secured, ascend further to Rohtang Pass (3,978m) to witness majestic glaciers, play in the snow, and click scenic pictures." },
